{"tid":2510754,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"港超聯今日8點有狗隻執法","createTime":"2021-04-30T11:17:56.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-30T17:19:54.000Z","uid":19847,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"607ce27224b63dc0f73f361990cbba3019af166b","tid":2510754,"uid":19847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T11:17:56.000Z","msg":"本身為交通警的廖國文（又名Siu Wan B），在去年 3 月於南區對和富大埔的一場賽事中，向其中一名和富大埔職員出示黃牌，有指當時有職員大罵「黑警」，因而被吹罰。而於前年 7 月沙田新城市廣場警民衝突後，他被指於 FB 發言批評示威者，被網民圍攻；之後廖國文未有再執法港超聯賽事，至疫情期間復賽後不久復出。執法港超聯賽事，至疫情期間復賽後不久復出。<br />\n<br />\n2021-04-30（五）東方龍獅 vs 冠忠南區 旺角大球場 20:00 $80 $30（東網免費直播）<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmTdivsPNYvcR7J4cwfEsNDPm5FhoL9SbSb1fb4kgT4puF?filename=wZ4pTJN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwZ4pTJN.jpg&h=c790dcf6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmPGrnTRVqXFL5oxuABXfi5hhULC7n5FHyjAUGWkZEzjVY?filename=XqpzSGV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXqpzSGV.png&h=184dee2b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6a3f5aabfb42e4d9f598e30fe8261f7d548edc4e","tid":2510754,"uid":133873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T11:18:10.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"1dd62d2d673477356d8f1447e4f8635245e58270","tid":2510754,"uid":19847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T11:18:53.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\"><strong>入場前記得填定網上健康申報表：</strong></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkfa.com/covid19/form\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkfa.com%2Fcovid19%2Fform&d=SQXEpmicj55cx%2FeODTqnT1DHT90Y5dJ0llo76wtTvPU%3D&h=5796cf24\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkfa.com/covid19/form</a><br />\n<br />\n足總而家放寬觀眾席至座位數目嘅75%<br />\n樽裝同罐裝嘢飲唔入得，但可飲用杯裝同紙包裝飲品（由於保障個人衛生關係，場內唔提供即棄杯）<br />\n場內必須佩戴口罩，唔可以進食<br />\n無劃位<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\"><strong>入唔到場都有直播睇<br />\n東網免費直播</strong></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/我撐本地波-394422737419738\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F%E6%88%91%E6%92%90%E6%9C%AC%E5%9C%B0%E6%B3%A2-394422737419738&d=SQXEpmicj55cx%2FeODTqnT1DHT90Y5dJ0llo76wtTvPU%3D&h=7ecc5508\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/我撐本地波-394422737419738</a><br />\n<br />\n下半場開波前（9點）都可以入場"},{"pid":"d0587c8ffc3ddf804c377ced379367f720606cbd","tid":2510754,"uid":19847,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T11:19:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmZ1GpVnUGt3sj2uH74iqfVbfb6iLx9p1C3fUogJsUiHYB?filename=QQkOe8b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQQkOe8b.jpg&h=173f5fd0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"aaf325aaf4901cff5e8693029b46f900c557e254","tid":2510754,"uid":19847,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T11:20:10.000Z","msg":"去年反送中事件爆發，沙田新城市廣場七月發生警民衝突，有報道指廖國文事後在社交平台發表針對示威者言論，包括辱罵示威者等；事後，足總未有再安排這位國際球證執法港超聯，直至到今年三月，賽事改到將軍澳運動場閉門復賽，廖國文才獲「復職」，今日傑志對理文的港超聯是其季內第三場擔任主球證的賽事。<br />\n<br />\n今午有十多名傑志及理文球迷在小西灣運動場附近天橋觀戰，當他們獲悉賽事由廖國文為主球證後已有不少聲音；而兩隊球員對廖國文初段執法有頗多意見，場外楚聽到球員大罵，以示對其法的不滿。至於場外球迷也對廖判決有不多意見，當中多名球迷賽事期間，以至半場及完場後，也多次破口，包括以粗言大罵。<br />\nFrom: 蘋果<br />\n<br />\n\t<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/sports/20200924/MBH7KDDZ2JHXVNKXEMEFCPMHRU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fsports%2F20200924%2FMBH7KDDZ2JHXVNKXEMEFCPMHRU%2F&d=SQXEpmicj55cx%2FeODTqnT1DHT90Y5dJ0llo76wtTvPU%3D&h=54828eff\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fsports%2F20200924%2FMBH7KDDZ2JHXVNKXEMEFCPMHRU%2F&h=ced82c2a\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/sports/20200924/MBH7KDDZ2JHXVNKXEMEFCPMHRU/</a>"},{"pid":"af4c36054aa8efff1d04e57572cd6fe0f4f978a8","tid":2510754,"uid":19847,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T11:20:37.000Z","msg":"今場主裁判是正職為警察的廖國文，他於去年曾在社交網站上發表辱罵示威者言論，令另外9名註冊球證不具名聯署表明「廖國文不代表我」。<br />\n<br />\n廖國文的執法表現亦一直備受爭議，他在前季的護級大戰中，向凱景出示6面黃牌，最終凱景在少踢一人下大敗，賽後更被凱景球員包圍。他今仗亦引來兩隊職球員不斷投訴，流浪林嘉緯及飛馬吳文希先後向球證表示對判決不滿，其中吳文希更稱「嘩！掂下都要foul呀？」流浪教練團亦在比賽期間向後備裁判員投訴，「咁都唔吹？Late tackle呀！」<br />\nFrom: 獨立媒體<br />\n<br />\n\t<a href=\"https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1078538\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1078538&d=SQXEpmicj55cx%2FeODTqnT1DHT90Y5dJ0llo76wtTvPU%3D&h=f2d81815\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1078538&h=0f25a4cc\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1078538</a>"},{"pid":"0644505079bc6ab2dc1e8431dc67e6b8fcb0e962","tid":2510754,"uid":19847,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T11:21:04.000Z","msg":"屌你老母死黑警尿國聞"},{"pid":"b84594d8857fc4be4d3c5560e7eb4c716b2f3a03","tid":2510754,"uid":13343,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"0644505079bc6ab2dc1e8431dc67e6b8fcb0e962","tid":2510754,"uid":19847,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T11:21:04.000Z","msg":"屌你老母死黑警尿國聞"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T11:21:20.000Z","msg":"黑警死全家"},{"pid":"097c9801053fb478daa41d6ffe96e3e96bf56960","tid":2510754,"uid":112747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T11:23:56.000Z","msg":"用国安法拉哂d球迷lor"},{"pid":"3af267743abba5db5930419ef455be9af916ec50","tid":2510754,"uid":312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T11:25:57.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae7d10e937226e9b6be23c1fd07fe1a9b6e9b5a3","tid":2510754,"uid":19847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3af267743abba5db5930419ef455be9af916ec50","tid":2510754,"uid":312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T11:25:57.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T11:29:03.000Z","msg":"多謝支持"},{"pid":"dcd9b1e0580c974bee68311140497e5df0bcb7b4","tid":2510754,"uid":29010,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,